    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled with Beisan components, and rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The rear subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Riding on refreshed Bilstein B16 coilovers and factory Style 67 forged wheels, the suspension kinematics remain tight and responsive. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint correction required, while the interior showcases Nappa leather with no bolster wear. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
